n\r\nerror: aborting due to previous error\r\n\r\nFor more information about this error, try `rustc --explain E0080`.\r\nerror: could not compile `playground`\r\n\r\nTo learn more, run the command again with --verbose.\r\n\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/77353/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/77353/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}